<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1249920' id='t-1249920'>most powerfully.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1251920' id='t-1251920'>I just want to thank you, 
I'm sure, on behalf of all of us,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1254762' id='t-1254762'>for your extraordinary leadership
and for being here.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
21:08
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1257280' id='t-1257280'>Mr. President, thank you so much.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
21:09
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1258873' id='t-1258873'>AT: Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
21:10
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1259666' id='t-1259666'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
